So, I was delighted to try the amazing new STYLE iQ Hair Dryer by @sharkhomeuk! Not only does it look fabulous but they have applied their expertise in iQ technology to develop this high-performance hair dryer and set of intelligent stylers for fast, healthy drying for ALL hair types.
 
In this IGTV you can see how great this @sharkhomeuk hair dryer is to use. I especially love the ability to customise the heat settings and airflow. 
 
It’s fast drying, there’s no heat damage and the style lasts. At the same time it leaves my hair looking fabulous without any frizz for everyday looks as well as party and glammed up styles.
 
Buy yours now at www.sharkbeauty.co.uk or available at John Lewis – you can thank me later!

latestIgtvVideos.title: Chatting hair and hair concerns…
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
AD/ Worries about our hair affect us all and @umbertogiannini have fabulous products to help. 

The gorgeous @alice_inthe_looking_glass and I have very different hair and different hair concerns. Alice has beautiful thick hair but finds that it seems to stop growing past a certain point. However, my concerns are about thinning hair and hair loss.

The “Grow Long” range from @umbertogiannini has products to help us both. I have been using the shampoo, conditioner and Grow  Tonic from the range and Alice has been using the mask and scrub.

Watch our IGTV to see us discussing our issues and our experiences with these products.

#ugonme #umbertogiannini #hairconcerns #hairissues #hairigtv #hairtonic #hairscrub #hairmask #hairtreatment #haircare #veganhaircare #crueltyfreehaircare #hairgrowth

latestIgtvVideos.title: Hair Loss Awareness Month with BAMbeautiful
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
AD/ This month is Hair Loss Awareness month and this one is very relevant to me as over the last few years I have noticed this happening to me. 

I think this is due to a variety of factors - my hormones (being pier-menopausal) general life stress and having Covid earlier this year. 

So this fabulous range by @bambeautifulnaturalcare which is designed to promote thickness, shine and moisture to thinning hair was just what I needed. In my 
IGTV you can see the haircare routine I have been using with @bambeautifulnaturalcare and how impressed with it I am.

I also love that the range is made from naturally derived ingredients and is cruelty-free and vegan- friendly. Not to mention it looks fabulous in my bathroom….

I also want us to be able to talk freely and openly about this subject which affects so many of us. Let’s get the chat going.

The @bambeautifulnaturalcare products are sold at @bootsuk online but also @bambeautifulnaturalcare and they currently have 25% off all products on their website.”

In case anyone is planning a trip to Reims or the Champagne area over the Summer 🍾

@ruinart was I think my favourite of the 2 tours we did and its also the oldest Champagne House. It was old school luxury done so beautifully and obviously the Champagne was amazing.

We were in a group of about 10 and our guide was superb. We learnt about the history of the house, had a tour of their vast historic chalk cellars (designated as a UNESCO World Heritage Site) whilst learning all about how they make their champagne and then back to a beautiful room where we got to taste 🥂

You can then visit their shop and we stayed for lunch at the restaurant in the grounds which was lovejy (and the food was reasonably priced!)

We walked here from our hotel in Reims and this was only half an hour though you can obviously take a taxi or book an uber. It was very popular so definitely book in advance. 

📍4 Rue des Crayéres, Reims 
Save for when you visit 🍾
